# Scripts layout

## Entrypoints

| Lane | Directory | Role |
|------|-----------|------|
| Auth | `scripts/auth/` | Headed login → `.auth/*.json` |
| Source | `scripts/source/` | Aggregator runners + Notion payload prep |
| Scrape | `scripts/scrape/` | Description scrape CLIs |
| Fill | `scripts/fill/` | URL health + application fill |
| Shared | `scripts/shared/` | `cleanup-data`, unified `run-log-basename` |
| Tests | `scripts/test/source/` | Session preflight (`test:access`) only |

## Libraries (`scripts/lib/`)

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `browser/` | Playwright launch + env bootstrap |
| `job/` | SourcedJob, scratch, screening, limits |
| `notion/` | Tracker constants, parsers, payloads |
| `artifacts/` | Scrape/fill JSON envelopes |
| `aggregators/` | Wobo, Handshake, Jack |
| `scrape/` | Extraction, Workday, language, markdown |
| `fill/` | Fill references + ATS heuristics |
| `cli-json.ts` | Shared stdin/file JSON helpers |
| `paths.ts`, `cleanup.ts`, `run-log.ts`, `url-health.ts` | Cross-lane utilities |

## When adding a script

1. Place the entrypoint under the matching lane folder
2. Put shared logic under the matching `scripts/lib/` subfolder
3. Register an npm script in `package.json`
4. Update the relevant skill’s `protocol/repository-scripts-map.md`
